results.p: The Yu-Gi-Oh! World Championship 2024 is a closed event, and is viewable by livestream only. On-site viewing and Public Events will not be available.
A popular Japanese anime and manga franchise from Kazuki Takahashi that mainly involves characters who play a card game called Duel Monsters.
